{"tid":1385241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一個生意人...我第一次起連登開post","createTime":"2019-07-30T04:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T05:45:26.000Z","uid":103992,"like":66,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7d90836a2a8f8c6a03b736ea74e951e9c09b78ec","tid":1385241,"uid":103992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:39:25.000Z","msg":"故然緊張，成日覺得連登乜都鬧。<br />\n公司罷工由我帶起，一直指向林奠政權，元朗白衣人單野睇住live激到我彈起火滾，直到尋日3:00坐實睇國務院記招緊張到貼住黎聽（因為國語唔叻）聽住會唔會有老解。<br />\n我發現我真係好愛香港，更加可憐後生既你地行到咁前，你地真係好勇敢。<br />\n到尋日有後生話無錢食飯，我個心真係好傷好痛，我可以做就係課金再課金，再睇下愈來愈多新聞講官黑勾結，我問自己到底香港點解變成咁，好似番左60年代。而家係香港既非常時期，比任何野都更重要，我認我無用我企唔到最前，但我地會有一日一齊慶祝，至少林奠要認輸，7婆搞到香港人咁，你同黑警同何妖都要做街老鼠！！現在唯有繼續心情沉重住先！！我仲頂到!"},{"pid":"67418940decf7d28698b17c890b9a959fb7bf219","tid":1385241,"uid":109706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:41:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"db5c7c1ced08255b3fd3f52ec7dd1efba8ce389e","tid":1385241,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:41:25.000Z","msg":"自貼老細位"},{"pid":"78091ceacfdf704b6599b3d6fab0af427098f0ec","tid":1385241,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:42:37.000Z","msg":"5/8"},{"pid":"3931fef54e3a2e96c51a892806e37cec71252074","tid":1385241,"uid":276609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:43:00.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"e7fbf60cb4f24dd830f166ded340b26afaa035af","tid":1385241,"uid":17796,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:43:06.000Z","msg":"用你嘅影響力，叫醒更多香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35cf9dc9d3f126477aebdf8f17d160de854bb87b","tid":1385241,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:43:10.000Z","msg":"匿名地認證你係老細身份先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7290ebae3ed5e499600fca62efdca00cd75d06","tid":1385241,"uid":49525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:43:21.000Z","msg":"大家不要再互相指罵了，我們都是愛護香港的市民，看見你們互相攻擊我很心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我們的特首林鄭月娥才是罪魁禍首，現在民怨沸騰又唔出來平息，又唔肯回應市民的訴求，搞到大家返唔到工。香港的經濟和樓價都被林鄭月娥拖跨，民不聊生，林鄭月娥真係千古罪人。"},{"pid":"1fa1387796ffcac26107a1965ed151d49a1824bb","tid":1385241,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:46:47.000Z","msg":"老細，林鄭只係傀儡<br />\n佢落台其實乜都唔會變"},{"pid":"323374ace4f1b7cbb56b19b2ec93b0b4b24c976a","tid":1385241,"uid":109794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:47:02.000Z","msg":"我地都好愛HK<br />\nBTW<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請入 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dsPmtT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dsPmtT</a> 一齊report 9 藍絲 fb pages!!!!!<br />\n一人一Report, 搞到佢地摺埋!!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4cdf0d9b23dd3e586b23b30a3c9b0b1ca399931b","tid":1385241,"uid":272178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:47:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"854ffd56f1d9e25dcd8945c622c39b1fd8363670","tid":1385241,"uid":103992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1fa1387796ffcac26107a1965ed151d49a1824bb","tid":1385241,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:46:47.000Z","msg":"老細，林鄭只係傀儡<br />\n佢落台其實乜都唔會變"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:53:03.000Z","msg":"根本所有人都係傀儡，中聯辦跳過蘆偉直接聯阿二都夠膽死。講番正題先：我見到林奠似隻死狗佢唔能夠再企出黎，或者你都岩，但林奠已經無法施政了係事實了。但推張見宗鬧狗又罷明唔俾佢坐正啦，所以只會空降一條建制底既傀儡，我想起馬要佢認輸，唔好話年年考第一。"},{"pid":"f7b1f195769dbea12e6747bd3ef83cf8682d9b01","tid":1385241,"uid":103992,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e7fbf60cb4f24dd830f166ded340b26afaa035af","tid":1385241,"uid":17796,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:43:06.000Z","m